As a mother,
I am always worried about him.

22
00:01:26,586 --> 00:01:28,129
How can I say this?

23
00:01:28,213 --> 00:01:29,881
He has a good heart.

24
00:01:29,964 --> 00:01:32,550
He's a… good person.

25
00:01:32,634 --> 00:01:35,762
He never gave me any trouble
when he was a kid.

26
00:01:35,845 --> 00:01:38,431
Si-won can give me
a bit of a headache sometimes.

27
00:01:39,140 --> 00:01:41,351
But he has a very kind heart.

28
00:01:41,434 --> 00:01:42,435
Mom…

29
00:01:44,187 --> 00:01:45,063
can I…

30
