ask you something?

31
00:01:47,357 --> 00:01:48,691
Mm.

32
00:01:49,317 --> 00:01:52,153
<i>Everyone has the power</i>
<i>to write their own story.</i>

33
00:01:52,237 --> 00:01:54,239
<i>But fate can change everything.</i>

34
